      "matters": "PETITION FOR LETTERS OF ADMINISTRATION<br>Off Calendar Apr-16-2008 Granted Per Written Order<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: Cynthia Schreurs for Marie King.<br><br>The Court stated that there was an issue with granting full authority as the Administrator appointed herself under the Power Of Attorney. Therefore, the Court granted the petition with limited authority, (signing the order for the same in open court).<br><br>Judge Pro Temp: Sue M. Kaplan. Reporter: Katy Bersamin, CSR#11722. Clerk: Rosie Noguera/ S. Ravinantapricha. Bailiff: Deputy J. Garrido.",
      "location": "CIVIC CENTER COURTHOUSE ROOM 204",
