    },
    {
      "court_date": "2008-03-19 9:00 AM",
      "matters": "PETITION FOR LETTERS OF ADMINISTRATION<br>Off Calendar Mar-19-2008 Continued To Apr-16-08 At 09:00 A.M. In Dept 204<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: Cynthia Schreurs for Marie King and Pamela Pritchard.<br><br>Ms. Schreurs addressed the examiner's notes. Ms. Schreurs reported that Ms. Pritchard was medically unable to sign, but that she was very coherent and that she nominated the attorney to act. In addition, she stated that the only asset was a half-interest in a house and that there were no plans to sell. The Court will notify the Public Guardian to review the matter. The matter was continued to April 16, 2008.<br><br>Judicial Officer: Judge John Dearman; Reporter: Katy Bersamin CSR #11722;  Bailiff: F. Smith; Clerk: Rosie Noguera.",
